 care. </p><p>The full, updated online <a href="https://www.safercaretexas.org/resources/abatingmaternalmortality/" target="_blank">Curriculum</a>– includes Pre-Test, PowerPoint with Instructor Notes &amp; Lesson Plan, Post Test, Health Literacy Jeopardy and Reflection Paper &amp; Rubric.</p><ul>  <li><a href="../files/2020/05/Ask-Me-3-English.pdf" target="_blank">Ask Me 3</a> English Handout</li>  <li><a href="../files/2020/05/Ask-Me-3-Spanish.pdf" target="_blank" >Ask Me 3</a> Spanish Handout</li>  <li><a href="../files/2020/05/What-About-Mom-English.pdf" target="_blank">What About Mom</a> English Handout</li>  <li><a href="../files/2020/05/What-About-Mom-Spanish.pdf" target="_blank">What About Mom</a> Spanish Handout</li>  <li><a href="../files/2020/05/What-About-Mom-QR-Code.png" target="_blank">What About Mom</a> QR Code</li>  <li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/what-about-mom/id1567761423" target="_blank">What About Mom</a> app</li>  <li><a href="https://rise.articulate.com/share/KDx7-AaNso9w3x77U4TRMzf10dEAY-Fn#/" target="_blank">Interactive Cultural Competency Training</a></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p></div></div><?php include('../../../incl/footer.html'); ?>